{"lemma":"عَلْكِ","slug":"عَلْكِ","root":"ع.ل.ك","root_slug":"ع-ل-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ل-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30327","n30328","n30329"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D9%83%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to chew, to knead with the teeth, to champ"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to tighten the hands upon from stinginess, to manage strictly, to tend well"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to prattle, to blather"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fix or fasten with resin"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَلَكَ (ʕalaka) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"resin, mastix, gum, chewing gum and the like"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"viscose, glutinous, which can be chewed long, sticky and slimy","examples":[{"text":"إن أرض مصر رملية لا تصلح للزراعة، لكنه يأتيها طين أسود علك فيه دسومة كثيرة يسمى الإيليز؛ يأتيها من بلاد السودان مختلطًا بماء النيل عند مده، فيستقر الطين، وينضب الماء، فيحرث ويزرع. وكل سنة يأتيها طين جديد، ولهذا يزرع جميع أراضيها ولا يراح شيء منها، كما يفعل في العراق والشام.","english":"The land of Egypt is sandy and unsuitable for agriculture, but to it comes a black viscose mud of much richness called ʾiblīz; it comes from the lands of the Sudan mingled with Nile water at rising tide, and the mud having settled and the water having drained one can plough and sow. And every year new mud comes to it and most of the regions of Egypt are sown by this, and it wanes by no jot, unlike it does in Iraq or Syria."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30327","headword_ar":"عِلْكٌ","root":"Elk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Resin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain thing that is chewed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Samog","text_ar":"صَمْغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sanawobar","text_ar":"صَنَوْبَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arozap","text_ar":"اَرْزَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusotuq","text_ar":"فُسْتُق"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarow","text_ar":"سَرْو"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yanobuwt","text_ar":"يَنْبُوت"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buTom","text_ar":"بُطْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the last of which is the best of these; (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lubaAn","text_ar":"لُبَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frankincense"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is chewed and is not thereby liquefied;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heating, diuretic, and strengthening to the venereal faculty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Samog","text_ar":"صَمْغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is chewed, consisting of frankincense"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lubaAn","text_ar":"لُبَان"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of other sorts, and that does not flow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in consequence of its being chewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) pl. [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuluwkN","text_ar":"عُلُوكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolAakN","text_ar":"اَعْلاَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n30328","headword_ar":"عَلَكٌ","root":"Elk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaAkN","text_ar":"عَلَاكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EulaAkN","text_ar":"عُلَاكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(accord. to some copies of the K, but not in the O nor in the TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tree of El-Hijáz:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species of trees growing in the region of El-Hijáz:"},{"kind":"text","text":"AHn says, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealak","text_ar":"عَلَك"},{"kind":"text","text":"are certain trees, of the characteristics of which I have not heard a description. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n30329","headword_ar":"عَلِكٌ","root":"Elk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"Food"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard to chew;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAlikN","text_ar":"عَالِكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [And] A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"viscous, glutinous, cohesive, sticky, ropy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slimy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"thing. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiynapN EalikapN","text_ar":"طِينَةٌ عَلِكَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth, green,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a dark"},{"kind":"text","t